{"id":63773,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/有文化的煤老板/","date":"2010-04-26T10:31:20Z","modified":"2010-04-26T10:31:20Z","title":"有文化的煤老板","content":"<p>早上坐摆渡去玛莎葡萄酒庄园岛（Martha’s Vineyard），我发现MV的海鸥很有文化，知道怎么弄到好吃的：<br />\n<img alt=\"bird feed-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/bird-feed-s.jpg\" title=\"bird feed-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>我跟海鸥学了两招，上岛后弄了辆敞篷吉普车当座驾，很拉风吧？<br />\n<img alt=\"jeep-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/jeep-s.jpg\" title=\"jeep-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>MV是有文化的煤老板们住的地方。有文化的煤老板不玩卡拉OK，人家玩土摩托：<br />\n<img alt=\"bike-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/bike-s.jpg\" title=\"bike-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>有文化的煤老板不玩藏獒，人家玩马：<br />\n<img alt=\"horse-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/horse-s.jpg\" title=\"horse-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>有文化的煤老板不玩小姐，人家玩过家家：<br />\n<img alt=\"beach party-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/beach-party-s.jpg\" title=\"beach party-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>有文化的煤老板不在北京上海买豪宅，人家在荒岛买小木屋：<br />\n<img alt=\"mirror-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/mirror-s.jpg\" title=\"mirror-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>有文化的煤老板不喜欢当政协委员，人家喜欢闲云野鹤：<br />\n<img alt=\"light house and lady-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/light-house-and-lady-s.jpg\" title=\"light house and lady-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>有文化的煤老板不喜欢吃肉，人家喜欢吃草：<br />\n<img alt=\"salad-s\" height=\"367\" src=\"http://www.immusoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/salad-s.jpg\" title=\"salad-s\" width=\"550\"></p>\n<p>吃完草，我回旅馆泡了个热水澡。泡澡的时候我使劲儿想了想，你猜怎么着？我真的不介意过有文化煤老板们过的日子。</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}